C.R. Bard Agrees to Buy ClearStream for 43.8 Million Pounds

-- B y   D a v i d   A l t a n e r
-- 
2011-09-20T06:07:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/c-r-bard-agrees-to-buy-clearstream-for-43-8-million-pounds.html
The boards of C.R. Bard Inc. and
 ClearStream Technologies Group Plc (CTN)  said they agreed the terms of
a recommended cash offer for ClearStream, to be made by an Irish
subsidiary of Bard. The offer would value ClearStream at about
43.8 million pounds.  To contact the reporter on this story:
David Altaner in London at 
 daltaner@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chris Peterson at 
 cpeterson@bloomberg.net  